/* Method Hiding =>  Use with Inheritance
Child class ka method parent class ke method ko hide krta he.
use new keyword with child class.nhi lagayge to warnig aaygi.
jab base class or derived class ke under same method ho tb method hiding hoti he.

child class ke under parent class ke method ko call krne ke tarike = >
1 use base keyword
2 cast child type to parent type and invoke the hidden member
3 parentclass pc = new childclass);
pc.hiddenmethod;

when we create the obj of child class, parent class obj is also created.

*/
